OL,3,CGuernsey rules out joint Air Display
OL,4,Cas Jersey fights for funding
OL,6,FJersey International Air Display needs
OL,7,Fmore financial support if it is to
OL,8,Fremain a staple in the island's
OL,9,Fcalendar, according to organisers.
OL,11,FThe 2024 scaled down event entertained
OL,12,Fthousands of spectators but of the 14
OL,13,Fplanes originally rostered, only 10
OL,14,Fmade it to the skies.
OL,16,FLast month, event organisers also set
OL,17,Fa crowdfunding target of #50,000 but
OL,18,Ffell short, bringing in #31,000.
