OL,3,CGuernsey rules out joint Air Display
OL,4,Cas Jersey fights for funding
OL,6,FOrganiser Mike Higgins says the budget
OL,7,Fis the key issue affecting the Air
OL,8,FDisplay.
OL,10,FHe adds: "If we're going to keep
OL,11,FJersey as a tourism destination and to
OL,12,Fhave free activities for islanders, we
OL,13,Fneed to support the air show."
OL,15,FMike says organisers are in
OL,16,Fdiscussions with potential sponsors,
OL,17,Fthe private sector and the Government
OL,18,Fto ensure the survival of the show.
