OL,3,CGuernsey rules out joint Air Display
OL,4,Cas Jersey fights for funding
OL,6,FHe also supports the idea of working
OL,7,Fwith Guernsey's Air Display, saying:
OL,8,F"We have aircraft coming long
OL,9,Fdistances and the cost of bringing
OL,10,Fthem into the islands is expensive."
OL,12,FHowever, ITV News spoke to officials
OL,13,Fin Guernsey who say the two events
OL,14,Fcannot be combined as their funding
OL,15,Fmechanisms are "vastly different".
OL,17,FThe States of Jersey originally gave
OL,18,F#60,000 to the Air Display for the two
OL,19,Fprevious years but this was cut to
OL,20,F#40,000 for 2024.
