OL,6,FMike says "by and large" organisers
OL,7,Ffeel supported by the Government but
OL,8,Fadds: "Unless we can raise the money
OL,9,Ffrom private sponsorship or
OL,10,Fgovernment, displays will never be
OL,11,Fwhat they were."
OL,13,FThe budget for Jersey Air Display has
OL,14,Falso fallen over the last decade:
OL,16,FMike also responded to concerns about
OL,17,Fthe running of the festival, saying:
OL,18,F"Learn the facts of what it takes to
OL,19,Frun an air show before you make
OL,20,Fcomments.
